They have horns like this.

266
00:25:01,610 --> 00:25:03,820
It's you.

267
00:25:03,820 --> 00:25:06,370
It's you.

268
00:25:06,370 --> 00:25:09,630
It's you.

269
00:25:19,510 --> 00:25:21,820
What am I doing?

270
00:25:24,300 --> 00:25:26,840
I must be crazy.

271
00:25:34,830 --> 00:25:38,430
