You said I was responsible, right?

290
00:26:39,240 --> 00:26:43,560
♫ Even if it's once, that's alright ♫

291
00:26:44,690 --> 00:26:45,480
♫ It's okay ♫

292
00:26:45,480 --> 00:26:49,430
The responsibility for surviving alone.

293
00:26:49,430 --> 00:26:51,630
Yes.

294
00:26:51,630 --> 00:26:54,490
I'll work harder.

295
