♫ I will treasure it alone for a long time ♫

317
00:28:35,640 --> 00:28:39,370
♫ before this feeling wanes ♫

318
00:28:39,370 --> 00:28:43,130
♫ Take my hand ♫

319
00:28:43,130 --> 00:28:47,960
♫ So that I don't get weary ♫

320
00:28:47,960 --> 00:28:53,310
♫ Even if there are flowers without scents ♫

321
00:28:55,090 --> 00:28:59,890
♫ You will receive love. Because it's enough ♫

322
00:29:04,960 --> 00:29:11,650
♫ Even if your voice is cold and it is the last, it's okay ♫

323
00:29:12,420 --> 00:29:16,360
♫ Please let me hear your song ♫

324
00:29:16,360 --> 00:29:19,800
♫ So that I can continue living ♫

325
00:29:19,800 --> 00:29:27,400
♫ I will treasure it alone for a long time before this feeling wanes ♫

326
00:29:27,400 --> 00:29:31,180
♫ Take my hand ♫

327
00:29:31,180 --> 00:29:33,850
♫ So that I won't get weary. You take me all. ♫

328
00:29:33,850 --> 00:29:36,840
♫ You take me all. ♫

329
00:29:36,840 --> 00:29:41,010
♫ You take me all. ♫

