Amazingly, I slept well.

332
00:30:17,480 --> 00:30:19,500
Hong Yi Yeong!

333
00:30:19,500 --> 00:30:21,360
Hong Yi Yeong!

334
00:30:22,250 --> 00:30:25,090
While you were sleeping last night,

335
00:30:25,090 --> 00:30:29,190
I organized my thoughts by myself.

336
00:30:29,190 --> 00:30:33,930
Actually, I recalled a few memories

337
00:30:33,930 --> 00:30:37,820
I wasn't able to tell you.

338
