I don't know either why I stabbed him. I also don't know what the circumstances were before.

342
00:31:07,610 --> 00:31:11,530
I want to find out so I'll be gone for a while.

343
00:31:11,530 --> 00:31:14,310
I don't know if I can find out.

344
